flowchart LR
    A[Collect metrics<br/>CPU / Queue / Response Time] --> B[Evaluate rules]
    B --> C{Condition met?}
    C -->|Yes| D[Scale action<br/>Scale Out or In]
    C -->|No| A
    D --> E[Instance change and warm-up]
    E --> F[Cooldown<br/>Wait for changes to take effect]
    F --> G[Measure again]
    G --> A

    H[Caution]
    H --> H1[Oscillation if thresholds too close]
    H --> H2[Scaling ineffective if dependency is bottleneck]

    style A fill:#e0f2fe,stroke:#0284c7,color:#111
    style B fill:#e0e7ff,stroke:#4f46e5,color:#111
    style C fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#d97706,color:#111
    style D fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#16a34a,color:#111
    style E fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#16a34a,color:#111
    style F fill:#fee2e2,stroke:#dc2626,color:#111
    style G fill:#e0f2fe,stroke:#0284c7,color:#111
